essdate=2015-11-15|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202234213/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3970752,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://chronicle.com/article/Despite-Controversy-Israeli/125423/|title=Despite Controversy, Israeli University in West Bank Attracts Arab Students|author=Matthew Kalman|date=17 November 2010|accessdate=2015-11-15|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126180626/https://www.chronicle.com/article/Despite-Controversy-Israeli/125423/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cri">{{cite web|author1=张瑾|title=占领和“抵制”之下的巴以互动：人民带来和平希望|url=http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2013/07/31/6251s4201173.htm|website=国际在线|language=zh-cn|access-date=2015-11-15|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117020304/http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2013/07/31/6251s4201173.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这里甚至还有很大一批持左翼观点的教师<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/leftist-views-don-t-keep-professors-from-teaching-at-ariel-1.458869|title=Leftist views don't keep professors from teaching at Ariel|author=Chaim Levinson|publisher=Haaretz|date=17 August 2012|accessdate=2015-11-15|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117063833/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/leftist-views-don-t-keep-professors-from-teaching-at-ariel-1.458869|dead-url=no}}</ref>。预计2025年，会招收20000名学生<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariel.ac.il/en/about-the-center|title=About Ariel University|publisher=Ariel University|accessdate=13 September 2018|archive-date=2019-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190205014930/http://www.ariel.ac.il/en/about-the-center|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

