==和平会议==
2011年12，撒玛利亚阿里埃勒大学中心举办了一场名为“以色列/巴勒斯坦和平的最佳计划”的特别会议，联合穆斯林自由派共同对抗恐怖主义，推动巴以和平进程。来自以色列的犹太人、阿拉伯人和来自约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦权力机构控制地区的阿拉伯人参加了对话。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/151200|title=Israelis, Arabs Offer Solutions to the Conflict|work=Arutz Sheva|accessdate=25 July 2015|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411003759/http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/151200|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.jpost.com/DiplomacyAndPolitics/Article.aspx?id=251039, Right-wing, Palestinians brainstorm at Ariel parley]{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>活动的组织者，以色列人多伦·图兹（Doron Tzur）希望，以色列和巴勒斯坦进行和平对话，共同探索解决巴以问题的途径，达成双方都可以接受的协议，付诸全民公投，并让它成为现实。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://makor1.wee.co.il/?p=610|title=Account Suspended|publisher=|accessdate=25 July 2015|archive-date=2019-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723215948/http://makor1.wee.co.il/?p=610|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==国际交流和合作==
[[File:Ariell065.jpg|250px]]
阿里埃勒大学是[[国际大学协会|国际大学协会]]（IAU）的成员。<ref name="iau-aiu.net">{{cite web |url=http://www.iau-aiu.net/content/institutions |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501224946/http://www.iau-aiu.net/content/institutions |archivedate=2013-05-01 }} Member Institutions</ref>学校与全球51所大学和高等教育机构签订了合作协议，遍布[[美国|美国]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[法国|法国]]、[[德国|德国]]、[[巴西|巴西]]、[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]、[[哥斯达黎加|哥斯达黎加]]、[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]、[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]]、[[波兰|波兰]]、[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]、[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]]、[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]]、[[台湾|台湾]]和[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]<ref name="ReferenceA">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ariel.ac.il/images/stories/site/management/PublicRelations/divur/cooperation_with_academic_institutions_2012.pdf |title=Ariel University Center of Samaria, in cooperation with academic institutions around the world |access-date=2015-11-15 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224092947/http://www.ariel.ac.il/images/stories/site/management/PublicRelations/divur/cooperation_with_academic_institutions_2012.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="University-directory.eu">{{cite web|url = http://www.university-directory.eu/Israel/Ariel-University-Center-of-Samaria/Ariel-University-Center-of-Samaria-Scientific-Cooperation-and-Partners.html#.TosupHK8GuI|title = Scientific Cooperation and Partners | Ariel University Center of Samaria | Israel|publisher = University-directory.eu|accessdate = 25 October 2011|archive-date = 2019-10-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191016040717/https://www.university-directory.eu/Israel/Ariel-University-Center-of-Samaria/Ariel-University-Center-of-Samaria-Scientific-Cooperation-and-Partners.html#.TosupHK8GuI|dead-url = no}}</ref>。与[[加拿大|加拿大]][[多伦多大学|多伦多大学]]合作开办了[[工商管理学硕士|工商管理学硕士]]（MBA）课程<ref>{{cite web|url=http://translate.google.co.il/translate?sl=iw&tl=en&js=n&prev=_t&hl=iw&ie=UTF-8&layout=2&eotf=1&u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ariel.ac.il%2Fimages%2Fstories%2Fsite%2Fmanagement%2FPublicRelations%2Fpr%2Fcanada_isreal.doc|title=Google Translate|publisher=|accessdate=25 July 2015|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184550/http://translate.google.co.il/translate?sl=iw&tl=en&js=n&prev=_t&hl=iw&ie=UTF-8&layout=2&eotf=1&u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ariel.ac.il%2Fimages%2Fstories%2Fsite%2Fmanagement%2FPublicRelations%2Fpr%2Fcanada_isreal.doc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年，{{link-en|全球风险专业人士协会|Global Association of Risk Professionals}}在该校成立了分支机构，开设课程和国际会议交流<ref name="Ariel.ac.il">{{cite web|url = http://www.ariel.ac.il/Projects/garp//|title = The GARP site at the Ariel University Center of Samaria; The academic chapter of Israel|publisher = Ariel.ac.il|accessdate = 25 October 2011|archive-date = 2016-05-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503150318/http://www.ariel.ac.il/Projects/garp//|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2011年，学校与[[乌拉尔联邦大学|乌拉尔联邦大学]]签署了合作协议，在[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]附近建立了{{link-en|斯科尔科沃创新中心|Skolkovo innovation center}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://israelsk.com/en/venture_fair/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111207020053/http://israelsk.com/en/venture_fair |archivedate=2011-12-07 }} Your Way to Russian Silicon Valley</ref> 此外,该校还代表[[以色列科学与人文学院|以色列科学与人文学院]]与[[俄罗斯科学院|俄罗斯科学院]]开展合作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.academy.ac.il/english/asp/events/events_details.asp?event_id=89 |title=Bi-national Russian-Israeli workshop |publisher=Academy.ac.il |date=19 June 2005 |accessdate=24 September 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326105137/http://www.academy.ac.il/english/asp/events/events_details.asp?event_id=89 |archivedate=2012-03-26 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ariel.ac.il/management/research/ResearchActivities.aspx |title=Ariel University Center of Samaria |publisher=Ariel.ac.il |date=2 August 2006 |accessdate=25 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101215644/http://www.ariel.ac.il/management/research/ResearchActivities.aspx |archivedate=2011-11-01 }}</ref>

由于学校所处的特殊位置，阿里埃勒大学被排除在“{{link-en|地平线2020|Horizon 2020}}”以欧合作研究项目受益方之外。<ref>{{cite news|last=Herb|first=Keinon|title=Jerusalem and EU agree on formula that allows Israel to join Horizon 2020 project|url=http://www.jpost.com/Diplomacy-and-Politics/Jerusalem-and-EU-agree-on-formula-that-allows-Israel-to-join-Horizon-2020-project-333101|accessdate=21 December 2013|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211232856/http://www.jpost.com/Diplomacy-and-Politics/Jerusalem-and-EU-agree-on-formula-that-allows-Israel-to-join-Horizon-2020-project-333101|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然该校承担了许多欧洲研究项目，然而学校却没能从欧洲获得任何研究经费，也影响了该校和欧洲大学的合作<ref name="cri"/>。

==学术抵制==
鉴于阿里埃勒学院与巴伊兰大学的关系，2005年4月，英国大学教师协会曾对阿里埃勒学院的母体巴伊兰大学进行了抵制<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kcl.ac.uk/kis/unions/aut/council.htm |title=Report to members from the AUT national council |accessdate=22 May 2005 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060130124019/http://www.kcl.ac.uk/kis/unions/aut/council.htm |archivedate=2006-01-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是2005年5月的抵制很快被撤销<ref>{{cite news |date=26 May 2005 |url=http://education.guardian.co.uk/higher/worldwide/story/0,9959,1493084,00.html |title=Academics vote against Israeli boycott |work=The Guardian |location=London |accessdate=22 May 2005 |archive-date=2005-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050911011813/http://education.guardian.co.uk/higher/worldwide/story/0,9959,1493084,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年，{{link-en|西班牙住房部|Ministry of Housing (Spain)}}取消了该校学生参加2009年国际建筑设计竞赛的资格。[[西班牙政府|西班牙政府]]解释说，他们做出此项决定的原因是学校建立在巴勒斯坦被占领土上.<ref name="ynetboycott">[http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3779907,00.html Spain boycotts Ariel college for being in 'occupied territory'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3779907,00.html |date=20210126100939 }} Ynetnews.com, 22 September 2009.</ref> 。[[反诽谤联盟|反诽谤联盟]]要求西班牙政府和[[美国能源部|美国能源部]]取消对该校研究人员参与[[马德里|马德里]]国际太阳能竞赛的禁令。<ref name="israelnationalnews.com">[http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/Flash.aspx/171732 ADL: Stop Discrimination Against Ariel University] {{Wayback|url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/Flash.aspx/171732 |date=20181106143736 }} Arutz Sheva, 30 September 2009.</ref>

2011年初，165名以色列学者宣布，他们将对阿里埃勒大学进行抵制，以表达对以色列扩建定居点行为的抗议。他们在请愿书中写道，阿里埃勒不是以色列领土的一部分。<ref>[http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/01/20111918558150780.html Israel academics to boycott college] {{Wayback|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/01/20111918558150780.html |date=20110209144939 }} Aljazeera English, 9 January 2011.</ref>

